description:
This is a 7 minute workout called '5 min Yoga Break: Reset & Find Calm' from the channel SarahBethYoga.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Feeling stressed or anxious? Hit reset with this quick 5 minute Yoga Break to restore your mind & find calm. Use deep belly breathing to relieve tension from your body. Wake up your legs, feet and hamstrings with leg extensions then release the tension in your chest, belly and back in a reclined twist.
